      "side": 1,
      "message": "[🔴 Critical Issues] Line 58: Plural unfinished translations are skipped entirely because _is_empty_unfinished returns False whenever \u003ctranslation\u003e has child elements. Qt TS plural messages commonly use unfinished \u003cnumerusform/\u003e children, so export_untranslated.py will never expose them and import_translations.py cannot fill them, leaving plural UI strings permanently untranslated under the new workflow. Please add explicit plural support: export each numerus form, validate/import the same number of forms, and patch the \u003cnumerusform\u003e children while preserving the type\u003d\"unfinished\" removal semantics once filled.",
      "revId": "3a46e9f8483f0d873fcd777a4acdeae47cfd09df",
